headline.print_headline: Morocco Halts Judicial Accord With France in Spat
headline.main: Morocco Halts Judicial Accord With France in Spat

lead_paragraph: Morocco's Justice Ministry announced Wednesday the suspension of all judicial cooperation accords with France in a deepening spat between the two close allies.
